title: Key Flow: Issue Dispatch

workflow: "Workflow Store"
tracker: "Tracker Client"
orchestrator: "Orchestrator"
workspace: "Workspace Manager"
runner: "Agent Runner"
codex: "Codex App Server"
status: "Runtime Snapshot"

workflow -> orchestrator: supplies validated config
tracker -> orchestrator: returns active issues
orchestrator -> workspace: prepares issue workspace
orchestrator -> runner: dispatches issue
runner -> codex: starts thread and turn
codex -> runner: emits runtime events
runner -> orchestrator: reports completion / failure
orchestrator -> status: updates running and retry state
